the Messenger, and in whatever you have come with and instructed. So, (please) write us down with those who bear witness.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho aap par ay waliye Khuda, rehmate’n Khuda ho aur uski barkaat. Ay Ma’bood! Isko mere liye aakhri mauqa qaraar na de jo ziyarat ki hai mai ne Tere Nabi ke farzand aur Teri makhlooq par Teri hujjat ki. Mujhe aur unhe apni Jannat mein yekja (ek saath) kar de, mujhe mehshoor kar unke saath unke giroh mein, shaheedo’n aur neko’n ke saath aur yeh kitne achchhe ham-nasheen hai. Aap ko supurd karta hu, aap ki tawajjoh chahta hu aur aap ko salaam pesh karta hu. Ham imaan rakhte hai Khuda o Rasool par aur us par jo aap laaye aur uski taraf rehbari ki, pas ay Khuda hamein gawaho’n mein likh de.", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA WALIYYALLAA-HE WA RAHMA-TULLAAHE WA BARAKAATO-HU. ALLAAHUMMA LAA TAJ-A’L-HO AAKLHERAL A’HDE MIN ZIYAARA-TIBNA NABIYYEKA WA HUJJATEKA A’LAA KHALQE-KA WAJMA’NEE WA IYYAAHO JANNATE-KA WAHSHUR-NEE MA’HU WA FEE HAZBEHI MA-A’SH SHOHADAA-E WAS-SAALEHEENA WA HASONA OOLAAA-E-KA RAFEEQAN WA ASTAWDE-O’KAL LAAHO WA ASTAR-E’EKA WA AQRAO A’LAIKAS SALAAMO. AAMANNAA BILLAAHE WA BIR-RASOOLE WA BEMAA JETA BEHI WA DALALTA A’LAIHE FAKTUBNAA MA-A’SH SHAAHE-DEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسّلَامُ عَلَیْکَ یَا وَلِیَّ اللہِ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَ بَرَکَاتُہٗ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ لَا تَجْعَلْہُ اٰخِرَ الْعَہْدِ مِنْ زِیَارَتِیْ ابْنَ نَبِیِّکَ وَحُجَّتِکَ عَلٰی خَلْقِکَ وَاجْمَعْنِیْ وَ اِیَّاہُ فِیْ جَنَّتِکَ وَاحْشُرْنِیْ مَعَہٗ وَفِیْ حِزْبِہٖ مَعَ الشُّہَدَآئِ وَالصَّالِحِیْنَ وَحَسُنَ اُوْلٰٓئِکَ رَفِیْقًا وَاَسْتَوْدِعُکَ اللہُ وَاَسْتَرْعِیْکَ وَاَقْرَئُ عَلَیْکَ السَّلَامُ۔ اٰمَنَّا بِاللہِ وَبِالرَّسُوْلِ وَبِمَا جِئْتَ بِہٖ وَدَلَلْتَ عَلَیْہِ فَاکْتُبْنَا مَعَ الشَّاہِدِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": n